<br>
Answers are:<br>
<br>
1 - Who is the blue mage?  A:  Tenser<br>
<br>
2 - Who betrayed the Circle of Eight? A: Rary<br>
<br>
3 - What were the sphere, the cone and the cube for? A: to access different part of Lolth's Demonweb from the Descent to the Depths, Vault of the Drow and Queen of the Demonweb Pits series.<br>
<br>
4 - Who are Iuz's parents?  A:  Graz'zt, Demon Lord of Azzagrat and Iggwilv (female archmage who took over the Caverns of Tsjocanth, one of THE best D&amp;D modules ever)<br>
<br>
5 - Bonus question: Who is the One Who Shall Not Be Named?  A:  Tharizdun...the baddest mofo in the D&amp;D universe.<br>
